---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { BRAND, CONTACT_EMAIL } from "../consts";
---

<Base
  title={`About — ${BRAND}`}
  description={`${BRAND} builds free, privacy-first file tools that run entirely in your browser.`}
  path="/about"
>
  <section class="content prose">
    <h1>About {BRAND}</h1>

    <p>{BRAND} is a small project with a simple goal: make everyday file tasks — converting, combining, compressing — fast, free and private.</p>

    <h2>Privacy by design</h2>
    <p>Most online converters work by uploading your files to a server, processing them there, and sending them back. That is slow and means your documents pass through someone else's computer. We took a different approach: our tools run entirely in your browser using modern web technology. Your files are processed on your own device and never leave it. Nothing is uploaded, nothing is stored.</p>

    <h2>What we believe</h2>
    <p>Simple tools should be free, should not require an account, and should not bury you in watermarks or ads-before-you-can-click. We keep the tools clean and the experience fast, on any device.</p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>Have feedback or a tool you'd like us to build? Email us at <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a> — we read every message.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
